
BUILDING ZMAIL ON LINUX:

You'll need binary and devel packages for motif and libc-client.
On Debian: apt-get install libmotif-dev libc-client-dev
On Ubuntu 9.10 Karmic: apt-get install libmotif-dev libc-client2007b-dev

sh configure linux_glibc
sh mkmakes linux_glibc motif
make

To run in place:
export ZMLIB=/path/to/lib

